readme: # colorful-magenta-syntax theme This is a light and colorful theme with magenta font color for those who want a more colorful syntax theme. Theme could be installed in Atom or with apm install colorful-magenta-syntax ![A screenshot of your theme](https://i.ibb.co/QN9snS8/example-JS.png) Visit Project at https://atom.io/themes/colorful-magenta-syntax
